snippet.textDisplay: Well, I don't want nostalgia to get in the way of progress, but there's no real progress to be found in the series right now. The 64 version was a major upgrade from the original, and the Gamecube version gave much smoother controls, better visuals and a unique system, but after that it kind of stuttered.
